name: check_points
ddl: CREATE TABLE check_points (_id VARCHAR (30) PRIMARY KEY UNIQUE NOT NULL, last_ckp_id VARCHAR (30), next_ckp_id VARCHAR (30), conn_log_id VARCHAR (30) NOT NULL, children_chains_ids_json TEXT, children_items_ids_json TEXT, attached_file_ids_json TEXT, complete_level INT (10) NOT NULL, field_name VARCHAR (20), label VARCHAR (20) NOT NULL, create_time DATETIME NOT NULL, update_time DATETIME, "desc" TEXT);
